Starscream

"I don't know hot it happened. KitKat was skimpy on the details. She 
said she'd explain when we got back."

They travelled for a bit and than arrived at the base. Starscream 
popped the cockpit.

"Hop out!"

Trainers

"All right, it's game time," said Prebon, "Slayer, you start us off. 
Stay in cloak and hunt down the wolf. As soon as you open fire on 
him, we will attack the Ark. I think we will stay in cloak, and it 
will make them confused and by Blaze more time. Okay Slayer. Time to 
prove yourself. Destroy that wolf bot!"
